{"tid":966291,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【香港歷史】東江水是中國對香港的恩賜? 政治學者告訴你真正答案","createTime":"2019-01-02T16:26:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T13:59:24.000Z","uid":78029,"like":107,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"eb52cd39db4f64c4209cb528255728b65722cc57","tid":966291,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T16:26:01.000Z","msg":"大家好，小弟開咗個知識型Youtube channel ，希望分享吓有趣知識(心理學, 科學, 歷史, 甚至政治), 希望可以令香港Youtube多元化D<br />\n<br />\n今次繼續講吓香港歷史, 聚焦去睇東江水同香港供水系統如何生成, 從而拆解東江水係中國恩賜之類講法<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GiPkDPg7d04\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGiPkDPg7d04&d=OgrN6AVWjJ%2F4N5oe7cD%2Fz4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=2c64618c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GiPkDPg7d04</a><br />\n<br />\n上次講吓意志力, 由生理角度提升意志力的方法<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g4cN0cWQtB0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dg4cN0cWQtB0&d=OgrN6AVWjJ%2F4N5oe7cD%2Fz4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=e6798990\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g4cN0cWQtB0</a><br />\n<br />\n上次繼續講吓香港歷史, 聚焦去冷戰初期50年代的時勢點令到港英政府成立香港中文大學<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0GfzPr1IcvA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0GfzPr1IcvA&d=OgrN6AVWjJ%2F4N5oe7cD%2Fz4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=e4faf996\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0GfzPr1IcvA</a><br />\n<br />\n上上次講吓點樣溫暖輕鬆提高別人對你的評價, 輕鬆獲取信任!<br />\n如有不足, 麻煩指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MwZzePErpMg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMwZzePErpMg&d=OgrN6AVWjJ%2F4N5oe7cD%2Fz4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=7c16a59d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MwZzePErpMg</a><br />\n<br />\n上上上次講吓點樣用模仿輕鬆提高別人對你的好感,輕鬆獲取別人信任!<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PxalLMq_gqw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPxalLMq_gqw&d=OgrN6AVWjJ%2F4N5oe7cD%2Fz4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=332a0a22\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PxalLMq_gqw</a>"},{"pid":"b18ebf3552951d88cf23b93fd2c1caa8ae462955","tid":966291,"uid":78029,"like":34,"dislike":3,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T16:26:42.000Z","msg":"呢次講吓教科書唔會教的香港歷史, 例如未開埠前有香港人幫英軍補給, 香港人唔係大中華史觀講到咁愛國 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3VyGBBak9Qs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3VyGBBak9Qs&d=OgrN6AVWjJ%2F4N5oe7cD%2Fz4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=5b92b8ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3VyGBBak9Qs</a><br />\n<br />\n呢集講吓新學到的知識有幾快會被遺忘,  又會遺忘幾多, 同埋我地有咩方法去減少遺忘, 將學到的知識由短期記憶轉化成長期記憶<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gHNy4VD0nEA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgHNy4VD0nEA&d=OgrN6AVWjJ%2F4N5oe7cD%2Fz4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=ab66b2f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gHNy4VD0nEA</a><br />\n<br />\n呢集講吓科學界點睇「世界上有無外星人? 如果有, 點解外星人無和我們接觸?」呢個問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3ob8lj7OM5Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3ob8lj7OM5Q&d=OgrN6AVWjJ%2F4N5oe7cD%2Fz4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=412d212d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3ob8lj7OM5Q</a><br />\n<br />\n呢集想講吓近年科學點睇「成年後腦袋係咪不再進步, 只會退化?」呢個問題, 從而介紹吓 我地可以點樣增加記憶力<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=21byiVTSZhI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D21byiVTSZhI&d=OgrN6AVWjJ%2F4N5oe7cD%2Fz4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=a55c0948\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=21byiVTSZhI</a><br />\n<br />\n呢集由大腦科學角度講吓靈魂出竅/離體經驗係咩一回事, 科學界有無方法重現靈魂出竅<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JhjpNvT-U4g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJhjpNvT-U4g&d=OgrN6AVWjJ%2F4N5oe7cD%2Fz4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=70efd293\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JhjpNvT-U4g</a><br />\n<br />\n呢集由大腦科學角度講吓一D因為腦部受傷而成為奇才的人, 從而睇下未來科技有無可能將我地由普通人突然變成奇才<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eCEv3hfdco8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DeCEv3hfdco8&d=OgrN6AVWjJ%2F4N5oe7cD%2Fz4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=498dba04\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eCEv3hfdco8</a><br />\n<br />\n第一集係由大腦科學, 心理學角度講吓愛情行為, 例如點解分手咁痛苦, 點解開始拍拖時會睇唔到對方缺點: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mgTq1gYCsZA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DmgTq1gYCsZA&d=OgrN6AVWjJ%2F4N5oe7cD%2Fz4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=189a8b92\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mgTq1gYCsZA</a>"},{"pid":"958b186f7587406da50ec4d8799c8dfc8511d396","tid":966291,"uid":179835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T16:28:22.000Z","msg":"留名支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ed682160b97031e920e97cc7017cb6e07745e0c","tid":966291,"uid":134438,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T16:29:46.000Z","msg":"幾得意 樓主加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e439654735336372eb0a84e86c27f8ee5c38d2e","tid":966291,"uid":78029,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T16:30:25.000Z","msg":"補充: <br />\n1. 教科書一般都寫海水化淡廠係因為第二次石油危機導致成本過高而收皮, 但問題係官僚係咪會咁在乎成本效益呢?  又或者, 如果政治原因係令到獨立自主供水系統咁重要, 咁點解會因為錢作怪而海水化淡廠收皮?  唔擺返去中英談判到睇, 似乎根本好難解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0040817d8770f407e36f815823c765b2362f09fb","tid":966291,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T16:35:24.000Z","msg":"2. 可能有人問, 點解港府唔一早起自主供水系統? <br />\n呢個問題可以睇返另一集小弟整的<br />\n【香港歷史】冷戰初期, 英國想過放棄香港? 香港中文大學創校史<br />\n當中提到, 其實1957年時, 英國曾經諗過放棄香港, 咁話得想放棄, 當然唔會想長遠問題<br />\n所以好多政策係57 年打後爆出嚟的<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0860e002d9e7e164acb91efea0e664e5fb7db9b0","tid":966291,"uid":78029,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T16:38:24.000Z","msg":"3. 其實有時真係好佩服港英政治智慧, 港英用錢買水, 唔比佢宣傳做恩賜<br />\n如果唔係, 今日我地好難駁親中人士的講法, 至少今日依然可以話係商業交易<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6960997b08f0b8447e3b02fe276ccc59f897ffca","tid":966291,"uid":78029,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T16:41:51.000Z","msg":"4. 今日其實東江水係倒好多, 令到水庫, 水塘集水能力發揮唔到, <br />\n而且食水亦經香港水管滲漏好多, <br />\n扣除呢D因素, 再加上慳D, 我地未必咁需要依賴東江水???"},{"pid":"fe1e2b9e26b7dd7c53fd602ce2c07e07372cca4b","tid":966291,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"958b186f7587406da50ec4d8799c8dfc8511d396","tid":966291,"uid":179835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T16:28:22.000Z","msg":"留名支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T16:43:07.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4311e11bc9468b38452c6ad62275b2ad13a37e1c","tid":966291,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ed682160b97031e920e97cc7017cb6e07745e0c","tid":966291,"uid":134438,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T16:29:46.000Z","msg":"幾得意 樓主加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T16:43:50.000Z","msg":"多謝絲打意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港歷史係好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e8f8fd884850ea935749bca9d012b616cd3cf24","tid":966291,"uid":172507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-